Weather App

Description
This project is a Weather App that displays real-time weather forecasts. It was developed using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Users can input a city name to get the current weather information for that city. The app also provides a 5-day forecast for the entered city.

Features
Enter a city name to get real-time weather information.
View the current temperature, wind speed, and humidity.
Use the current location option to get weather information based on the user's location.
View a 5-day forecast for the entered city.

How to Use
1. Open the `index.html` file in a web browser.
2. Enter a city name in the input field and click the "Search" button.
3. Alternatively, click the "Use Current Location" button to get weather information based on your current location.

